description	"Jedi Knight:
The Jedi Knight has trained in all three styles of single-lightsaber combat and has a wide range of useful powers, including Force Jump 3.

^2Weaponry:
- Lightsaber
-- Medium / Strong / Fast Styles
-- Saber Defense (2)
-- Blaster Defense   (1)
-- EX Saber Throw (2) ^3[CS1]
-- 20% Less DMG

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (2)
- Pull (2)
- Sense (1)
- Speed (1)
- Absorb (1)
- Heal (1)

^8Attributes:
- BP Free Jumps
- Faster Movement
- Bunny Hop (1)
- Slow Faller
- Cortosis (1)
- Force Block / Focus (2)
- 1 Extra Life
"